<h3 class="amber lighten-4">Welcome {{user_name}}</h3>

<div class="row amber lighten-4">
  {{#if logged_in}}
    {{#each categories as |category|}}
    {{> category-details}}
    {{/each}}
  {{else}}
  <p class="padded">Welcome to Toolin' Around! Here you can post tools that you have available for your neighbors to borrow, and you can request to borrow tools from your neighbors.</p>
  <p class="padded">When you sign up, please select your neighborhood to find local tools in your area! (And don't worry, more neighborhoods will be added soon.)</p>
  <p class="padded">We hope this site will help you find exactly the tools you need, neighbor-to-neighbor.</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>




